sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Web
    participant API
    participant Queue
    participant Worker
    participant DB
    User->>Web: Configure evaluation
    Web->>API: Create run
    API->>DB: Freeze manifest
    API->>Queue: Enqueue job
    Worker->>Queue: Pull job
    Worker->>DB: Persist sample results
    API-->>Web: Stream live progress
    Worker->>DB: Persist aggregate and decision
